What Do I Eat?

Never go hungry

You’ll be enjoying 3 Jenny Craig meals and 2 snacks every day with over 60 menu options to chose from including 9 new items!

Lose weight whilst enjoying your favourite meals

With a Jenny Craig planned menu, you don’t have to worry about overeating. Each meal is perfectly positioned to help keep you satisfied while you slim down. Even your old favourites such as lasagna is on the menu.
